{"tid":2305152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】增 109 宗本地確診 三餐廳爆疫須強制檢測 筲箕灣方樹泉宿舍須撤離","createTime":"2020-11-29T11:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T12:36:19.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9dbd05055cb378311f826623223decb17a95f20","tid":2305152,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:36:16.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎第四波疫情首日破百，今（29 日）新增 115 宗確診，當中 109 宗為本地個案，其中 24 宗源頭不明，31 宗在社區檢測中心找到。另有 50 多宗初步陽性，確診者包括 73 女 42 男，年齡介乎 11 個月至 86 歲。歌舞群組再增 62 人，累計約 479 宗；另外出現餐廳群組，三間餐廳包括灣仔星月居、中環 8 1/2 Otto e Mezzo - Bombana 及上環泉章居大飯店，共有十多名員工、食客確診，食衛局將於明日發公告，要求在 11 月 15 日後曾到訪該些餐廳的入士接受強制檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%A2%9E-109-%E5%AE%97%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E4%B8%89%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E7%88%86%E7%96%AB%E9%A0%88%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E7%AD%B2%E7%AE%95%E7%81%A3%E6%96%B9%E6%A8%B9%E6%B3%89%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E9%A0%88%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25A2%259E-109-%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2596%25AB%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-%25E7%25AD%25B2%25E7%25AE%2595%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A8%25B9%25E6%25B3%2589%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E9%25A0%2588%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%259B%25A2%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGif2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=a2fbc522\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25A2%259E-109-%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2596%25AB%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AA%25A